result.title: Three Subregionals Cup Stage 1: Final Standings are published
result.content:
Two teams, solving Moscow subregional as testers, are added to standings of the first stage of Three Subregionals Cup. And after that final standings of Three Subregionals Cup are published.

Second stage of the Three Subregionals Cup is scheduled to Thursday, November 6, 2014, 12:00 Moscow Time. In case of any changes information will be added to this post.
